Play Air Wars Online

Air Wars is one of the most exciting air combat multiplayer games.
In this epic 3D war game, your goal is to defeat your opponents in air combat to capture the enemy base.
in Air Wars Fly and blast enemies under your throats. Then fight in a terrifying battle in the sky.
